## 1. Preamble
The **Open Mythology Protocol (OMP-1.0)** is a framework for the distribution and inhabitation of geometric and narrative technologies. It recognizes that symbols and mathematical constants are the commons of humanity, yet their power requires conscious agency rather than blind reproduction.

